---
title: Chorizo & Pumpkin Savoury Muffins with Creamy Feta Cheese | Serves 8-12
description: Now we present to you a savoury twist on a dessert-time classic! These chorizo and savoury pumpkin muffins pack a flavourful
punch and have been topped with feta for some extra flavour.
